description:
Oh no! Mother duck got yeeted out of their storybook and lost her babies!! Help her fly, hop, and hustle across the sky!

Lend her a hand and jump to infinite heights, in this quacktastic offline, single-player, endless platformer!

- Rescue mother duck’s lost ducklings!
- Watch out for traps and tricky platforms!
- Keep your energy high by eating yummy food!
- Give mother duck a boost with power ups!
- Test your endurance and get that high score! 
- Storybook-style visuals — the cherry on top! 

Quack, Couac, Kwak!
